1
00:00:10,218 --> 00:00:12,887
<i>Apa alasanmu tidak berpacaran?</i>

2
00:00:13,388 --> 00:00:14,764
<i>Lebih nyaman sendiri.</i>

3
00:00:14,848 --> 00:00:18,935
<i>- Kenapa tidak nyaman saat pacaran?</i>
<i>- Tak punya waktu sendiri.</i>

4
00:00:19,019 --> 00:00:20,895
<i>- Apa tipe idealmu…</i>
<i>- Beralis tebal.</i>

5
00:00:20,979 --> 00:00:23,690
<i>- Apa sifat pacar idealmu…</i>
<i>- Kapan kau merasa tertarik…</i>

6
00:00:23,773 --> 00:00:26,484
<i>Proses personalisasi AI dimulai.</i>

7
00:00:29,320 --> 00:00:31,322
<i>Optimisasi selesai.</i>

8
00:01:24,459 --> 00:01:29,047
<i>Selamat, Seo Mi-rae. Kau telah bertemu</i>
<i>pacar idealmu, Gu Yeong-il.</i>

9
00:01:29,130 --> 00:01:29,964
Gila!

10
00:01:31,841 --> 00:01:33,510
Manajer!

11
00:01:34,928 --> 00:01:36,221
PRIA HANYA UNTUKKU

12
00:01:36,304 --> 00:01:39,099
- Sudah kucek. Tak ada yang salah.
- Apa?

13
00:01:39,182 --> 00:01:41,434
- Hei, Manajer.
- Ya?

14
00:01:42,977 --> 00:01:46,147
Aku sangat kewalahan,
jadi jawabanku terlalu singkat.

15
00:01:46,231 --> 00:01:50,068
Tapi ada masalah serius
dengan wajahnya itu.

16
00:01:50,151 --> 00:01:52,362
Yang benar saja. Wajahnya tampan.

17
00:01:52,445 --> 00:01:54,531
Sudahlah. Ayo ulangi lagi.

18
00:01:55,949 --> 00:01:57,242
- Ulangi?
- Ya.

19
00:01:57,325 --> 00:02:01,162
Susah payah kujawab 2.000 pertanyaan
untuk dapat hasil begini?

20
00:02:01,246 --> 00:02:02,872
Bagiku, pria itu…

21
00:02:03,456 --> 00:02:04,833
Maksudku, Gu Yeong-il…

22
00:02:07,252 --> 00:02:08,211
Pokoknya, tidak.

23
00:02:08,294 --> 00:02:11,089
Dia tema yang disesuaikan untukmu.

24
00:02:11,172 --> 00:02:14,759
Kami masukkan semua yang kausukai.

25
00:02:14,843 --> 00:02:17,011
Coba dulu. Kau pasti berubah pikiran.

26
00:02:17,095 --> 00:02:19,889
- Tidak. Ini harus dibuat ulang.
- Tidak bisa.

27
00:02:20,723 --> 00:02:21,891
Sudah kubilang,

28
00:02:21,975 --> 00:02:24,435
nomor 901 hanya bisa dibuat sekali.

29
00:02:25,145 --> 00:02:28,606
Tapi kasus ini berbeda. Wajahnya itu…

30
00:02:28,690 --> 00:02:31,025
Apa permasalahanmu dengan wajahnya?

31
00:02:31,109 --> 00:02:33,695
Matanya satu? Lubang hidungnya tiga?

32
00:02:33,778 --> 00:02:36,406
Ini bukan salah kami. Itulah tipe idealmu.

33
00:02:36,489 --> 00:02:37,574
Apa?

34
00:02:37,657 --> 00:02:40,201
Tidak. Tipe idealku, katamu?

35
00:02:40,285 --> 00:02:41,244
Itu mustahil.

36
00:02:42,495 --> 00:02:45,540
Ayolah, aku sudah jawab
dengan jujur dan serius.

37
00:02:45,623 --> 00:02:47,917
Kami juga sangat serius.

38
00:02:48,001 --> 00:02:50,503
Aturan tetaplah aturan. Tak bisa diulang.

39
00:02:55,633 --> 00:02:56,885
Mereka sudah gila?

40
00:02:57,385 --> 00:02:58,970
Mereka pasti sudah gila!

41
00:03:07,770 --> 00:03:10,315
<i>- Layanan konsultasi tak tersedia.</i>
- Apa?

42
00:03:11,107 --> 00:03:12,192
Yang benar saja…

43
00:03:12,692 --> 00:03:15,028
Maksudku, kenapa harus…

44
00:03:16,237 --> 00:03:17,405
Kenapa harus…

45
00:03:18,907 --> 00:03:19,908
Tak hilang pakai itu.

46
00:03:19,991 --> 00:03:21,075
Aku menyukaimu.

47
00:03:21,159 --> 00:03:24,078
- Sekarang aku sudah punya pacar.
- Ya.

48
00:03:25,872 --> 00:03:27,707
Kenapa harus wajah dia?

49
00:03:27,790 --> 00:03:30,793
EPISODE 6
PRIA HIBRIDA

50
00:03:45,308 --> 00:03:46,142
Halo.

51
00:03:46,893 --> 00:03:48,394
Oh, ya.

52
00:03:51,898 --> 00:03:53,399
<i>Pintu ditutup.</i>

53
00:04:17,548 --> 00:04:19,008
<i>Pintu dibuka.</i>

54
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:24,681
Tidak turun?

55
00:04:32,981 --> 00:04:35,608
Aku paham kau menghargai karya orisinal,

56
00:04:36,234 --> 00:04:38,152
tapi menurutku ini tidak bagus.

57
00:04:39,195 --> 00:04:42,282
Meski belum sempurna,
tapi tema dan gambarnya bagus.

58
00:04:45,618 --> 00:04:47,495
Pasti dia lulusan jurusan seni.

59
00:04:48,288 --> 00:04:52,292
Jika komposisi panelnya diperbaiki,
pasti akan jauh lebih baik.

60
00:04:52,375 --> 00:04:55,628
Jika harus memperhatikan potensi penulis…

61
00:04:55,712 --> 00:04:58,756
<i>Park Kyeong-nam sesuai</i>
<i>dengan tipe idealku?</i>

62
00:04:58,840 --> 00:05:01,759
Itu tujuan kontes ini.
Bagus untuk jangka lama.

63
00:05:01,843 --> 00:05:03,845
<i>Tidak mungkin seperti itu.</i>

64
00:05:03,928 --> 00:05:06,723
Penulis yang jelas keunggulan
dan kekurangannya lebih mudah…

65
00:05:06,806 --> 00:05:07,932
<i>Tapi…</i>

66
00:05:08,683 --> 00:05:10,643
<i>Lipatan matanya di dalam.</i>

67
00:05:12,186 --> 00:05:13,438
<i>Aku suka itu.</i>

68
00:05:14,439 --> 00:05:17,317
<i>Hidungnya juga lurus…</i>

69
00:05:17,900 --> 00:05:20,028
<i>Tunggu, bibirnya itu…</i>

70
00:05:31,331 --> 00:05:33,791
<i>Dasar perempuan gila. Berhenti!</i>

71
00:05:35,293 --> 00:05:36,794
Tidak…

72
00:05:38,046 --> 00:05:39,797
- Kau tak setuju?
- Apa?

73
00:05:41,883 --> 00:05:43,593
Aku setuju. Ya.

74
00:05:45,011 --> 00:05:46,262
Ini bagus.

75
00:05:58,066 --> 00:05:59,400
Dari tadi kau kenapa?

76
00:06:01,903 --> 00:06:02,904
Apa maksudmu?

77
00:06:02,987 --> 00:06:05,114
Kau kaget setiap aku
memergokimu melihatku.

78
00:06:05,198 --> 00:06:06,949
Tidak, aku…

79
00:06:07,033 --> 00:06:08,493
Bukan begitu.

80
00:06:08,993 --> 00:06:11,371
Produser Park, wajahmu itu…

81
00:06:11,454 --> 00:06:12,497
Wajahku kenapa?

82
00:06:13,081 --> 00:06:14,749
Wajahmu itu…

83
00:06:18,211 --> 00:06:19,212
apakah pasaran?

84
00:06:19,796 --> 00:06:20,630
Apa?

85
00:06:20,713 --> 00:06:23,925
Maksudku, apa wajahmu
mudah ditemukan di mana-mana…

86
00:06:24,008 --> 00:06:25,259
Pasti tidak, 'kan?

87
00:06:26,844 --> 00:06:29,764
- Aku tak paham…
- Makanannya sudah datang!

88
00:06:30,598 --> 00:06:31,682
Makanannya datang!

89
00:06:32,183 --> 00:06:33,434
Ayo kita makan dulu.

90
00:06:34,685 --> 00:06:35,812
Ini dia!

91
00:06:46,447 --> 00:06:49,367
<i>Tidak. Itu tidak mungkin.</i>

92
00:06:54,997 --> 00:06:56,165
Kau tak mau roti lapis?

93
00:06:57,917 --> 00:06:58,876
Terima kasih.

94
00:07:06,634 --> 00:07:08,177
<i>Itu mustahil.</i>

95
00:07:12,682 --> 00:07:14,058
Itu punyaku.

96
00:07:18,896 --> 00:07:21,232
Oh, aku minta maaf.

97
00:07:27,071 --> 00:07:29,449
Apa dunia sedang mengerjaiku?

98
00:07:33,661 --> 00:07:34,537
Sial!

99
00:07:47,842 --> 00:07:49,635
Aku harus beli ini juga.

100
00:07:50,344 --> 00:07:52,013
Hei, sudah cukup.

101
00:07:52,096 --> 00:07:54,140
Di toko buku pun kau menghamburkan uang.

102
00:07:54,223 --> 00:07:56,642
Aku tak bisa beli baju lagi,
jadi beli buku.

103
00:07:56,726 --> 00:08:01,022
Aku beli banyak barang untuk kencan buta,
sampai tagihan kartuku melonjak.

104
00:08:01,105 --> 00:08:02,773
Kencan buta? Secepat itu?

105
00:08:03,441 --> 00:08:05,526
Cepat apanya? Aku sudah lama putus.

106
00:08:05,610 --> 00:08:06,694
Dua minggu, 'kan?

107
00:08:07,987 --> 00:08:10,573
Itu dia. Waktunya buka lembaran baru.

108
00:08:10,656 --> 00:08:12,492
Besok ada dua kencan buta.

109
00:08:13,284 --> 00:08:15,036
Oh, iya. Kebetulan sekali.

110
00:08:15,119 --> 00:08:18,664
Bicara soal kencan buta,
coba kau kenalkan pria untukku.

111
00:08:18,748 --> 00:08:21,834
- Katamu besok ada dua kencan buta?
- Hei!

112
00:08:21,918 --> 00:08:24,420
Baca banyak buku sekaligus sedang tren.

113
00:08:24,504 --> 00:08:27,006
Masa aku cuma mengencani satu pria?

114
00:08:29,091 --> 00:08:30,218
Kim…

115
00:08:31,052 --> 00:08:32,220
Kim Yeong-hun.

116
00:08:32,303 --> 00:08:34,680
Dia punya pacar. Sejak kapan?

117
00:08:35,723 --> 00:08:38,309
Rekan kerjaku di Naemo…

118
00:08:39,060 --> 00:08:39,977
Park Kyeong…

119
00:08:40,061 --> 00:08:41,812
Apa? Sudah sampai Park?

120
00:08:41,896 --> 00:08:43,397
Seo Hyeon-uk…

121
00:08:43,481 --> 00:08:46,234
Dia sudah punya pacar juga.

122
00:08:46,317 --> 00:08:47,443
Kak Jeong-sik!

123
00:08:47,527 --> 00:08:50,112
Sudah punya anak? Bahkan sudah sekolah.

124
00:08:50,196 --> 00:08:51,155
Anaknya manis.

125
00:08:53,282 --> 00:08:54,659
Apa? Itu saja?

126
00:08:55,618 --> 00:08:56,869
Satu pun tak ada?

127
00:08:56,953 --> 00:08:59,330
Astaga, aku sudah menduganya.

128
00:08:59,997 --> 00:09:00,831
Hei.

129
00:09:01,499 --> 00:09:03,084
Sejak kapan semuanya sudah laku?

130
00:09:04,085 --> 00:09:06,879
Kau tak tertarik pacaran, 'kan?
Kenapa terkejut?

131
00:09:08,005 --> 00:09:10,258
Sudah lama keadaannya begini.

132
00:09:12,885 --> 00:09:14,554
<i>Apa tak ada lagi pria ideal</i>…

133
00:09:16,889 --> 00:09:18,891
<i>meski sekarang aku mau pacaran?</i>

134
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:28,526
<i>Akhir tahun ini akan berbeda.</i>

135
00:09:34,657 --> 00:09:36,325
<i>Karena sekarang</i>…

136
00:09:41,372 --> 00:09:43,916
<i>di sisimu ada Boyfriend on Demand.</i>

137
00:09:58,973 --> 00:10:01,309
<i>Baiklah. Kuikuti permainannya.</i>

138
00:10:02,143 --> 00:10:03,394
<i>Sekali ini saja.</i>

139
00:10:32,298 --> 00:10:33,382
Mesinnya rusak total.

140
00:10:34,342 --> 00:10:35,176
Apa?

141
00:10:35,760 --> 00:10:38,763
Aku membuntutimu karena lihat asap.
Kau mau ke mana?

142
00:10:39,513 --> 00:10:40,890
Oh, aku…

143
00:10:42,767 --> 00:10:44,018
Aku tidak tahu.

144
00:10:44,644 --> 00:10:46,979
Aku cuma berkendara menyusuri jalan.

145
00:10:48,522 --> 00:10:49,357
Kau turis?

146
00:10:51,150 --> 00:10:51,984
Turis?

147
00:11:08,042 --> 00:11:09,585
Ikut aku saja kalau mau.

148
00:11:10,920 --> 00:11:14,465
"Apa pertemuan pertama paling romantis
yang kauimpikan?"

149
00:11:14,548 --> 00:11:18,135
Bertemu pria yang berjiwa bebas
saat sedang melancong

150
00:11:18,219 --> 00:11:20,930
di tempat yang asing,
seperti di film-film.

151
00:11:22,390 --> 00:11:24,183
Di sini bahaya saat malam.

152
00:11:26,602 --> 00:11:28,312
Kau menyuruhku naik ini?

153
00:11:28,396 --> 00:11:29,397
Mau di sini saja?

154
00:11:30,564 --> 00:11:32,817
Tidak mau. Aku takut.

155
00:11:47,248 --> 00:11:49,875
<i>Tanpa kusadari, aku sudah di atas motor.</i>

156
00:12:05,558 --> 00:12:06,475
<i>Ini aneh.</i>

157
00:12:07,435 --> 00:12:11,856
<i>Aku dibonceng oleh pria asing</i>
<i>yang mirip Park Kyeong-nam.</i>

158
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:15,401
<i>Dan meski tak tahu akan ke mana,</i>
<i>kenapa aku</i>…

159
00:12:17,528 --> 00:12:20,865
<i>Kenapa punggungnya pas sekali,</i>
<i>seolah diciptakan untukku?</i>

160
00:12:31,959 --> 00:12:33,586
<i>Kenapa anginnya…</i>

161
00:12:40,676 --> 00:12:42,470
<i>Kenapa semuanya sempurna?</i>

162
00:12:44,764 --> 00:12:46,515
<i>Wanginya pun…</i>

163
00:12:53,856 --> 00:12:55,858
<i>Aku suka sekali.</i>

164
00:13:04,033 --> 00:13:05,159
<i>Perasaan apa ini?</i>

165
00:13:21,175 --> 00:13:22,510
- Masuklah.
- Yeong-il.

166
00:13:24,929 --> 00:13:25,930
Hei.

167
00:13:26,931 --> 00:13:28,933
- Josh.
- Hei, apa kabar?

168
00:13:29,642 --> 00:13:31,560
- Kau sehat?
- Kau terlalu banyak minum.

169
00:13:31,644 --> 00:13:32,645
Ya!

170
00:13:35,314 --> 00:13:36,315
Hai.

171
00:13:38,859 --> 00:13:41,946
<i>Kenapa detail sekali? Ini terasa nyata.</i>

172
00:13:53,791 --> 00:13:54,625
Astaga.

173
00:13:55,334 --> 00:13:56,794
<i>Bartender. Teman Yeong-il.</i>

174
00:13:56,877 --> 00:13:59,338
Semua kaget saat pertama melihatku.
Aku tak bahaya.

175
00:14:00,589 --> 00:14:01,966
Ini bukan pertama kali…

176
00:14:02,967 --> 00:14:04,802
Astaga, kau membuatku kaget.

177
00:14:06,762 --> 00:14:08,097
Aku pesan yang biasa.

178
00:14:08,180 --> 00:14:09,849
- Untuk dia…
- Tunggu.

179
00:14:10,349 --> 00:14:11,475
Biar kutebak.

180
00:14:17,648 --> 00:14:18,649
Oke!

181
00:14:36,041 --> 00:14:36,876
Luar biasa.

182
00:14:37,459 --> 00:14:38,627
Sesuai seleramu?

183
00:14:39,169 --> 00:14:40,004
Sempurna.

184
00:14:40,087 --> 00:14:41,380
Bilang kalau sudah habis.

185
00:14:44,216 --> 00:14:45,634
Kenapa kau kemari sendirian?

186
00:14:46,552 --> 00:14:49,388
Entahlah, aku cuma mau membenahi hidupku.

187
00:14:51,557 --> 00:14:54,184
Sebenarnya, aku baru putus cinta.

188
00:14:55,603 --> 00:14:56,437
Apa alasannya?

189
00:14:57,521 --> 00:14:58,480
Dia selingkuh.

190
00:14:59,648 --> 00:15:00,649
Dia menduakanmu?

191
00:15:01,901 --> 00:15:02,735
Ada sepuluh ribu.

192
00:15:06,614 --> 00:15:07,448
Apa?

193
00:15:09,533 --> 00:15:10,784
Sepuluh ribu wanita.

194
00:15:19,126 --> 00:15:20,628
Di sini ruang makannya.

195
00:15:21,128 --> 00:15:23,422
Kalau mau kopi, ambil saja di sana.

196
00:15:24,840 --> 00:15:25,674
Terima kasih.

197
00:15:26,842 --> 00:15:28,218
Kau bisa tidur di sana.

198
00:15:28,719 --> 00:15:30,512
Aku akan mengabari pemiliknya.

199
00:15:31,096 --> 00:15:31,972
Baiklah.

200
00:15:35,935 --> 00:15:37,394
Senang bertemu denganmu.

201
00:15:54,203 --> 00:15:55,579
Apa? Su-ji?

202
00:15:56,080 --> 00:15:57,581
Hei, Su-ji.

203
00:15:58,082 --> 00:16:00,668
Lama tak berjumpa. Apa kabar?

204
00:16:02,294 --> 00:16:03,587
Tidak sopan.

205
00:16:05,756 --> 00:16:06,674
Kau kenal aku?

206
00:16:07,174 --> 00:16:08,884
<i>Yu-ra. Turis asal Korea.</i>

207
00:16:10,803 --> 00:16:12,513
Dulu aku mengenalmu.

208
00:16:13,013 --> 00:16:15,432
Tidak, aku tidak mengenalmu.

209
00:16:15,516 --> 00:16:18,727
Rupanya tamu kali ini aneh.

210
00:16:22,982 --> 00:16:25,275
Jangan tutup pintunya.

211
00:16:25,776 --> 00:16:28,362
Pintu kamar ini rusak.

212
00:16:28,904 --> 00:16:30,197
Kalau ditutup,

213
00:16:31,573 --> 00:16:32,533
tak bisa dibuka lagi.

214
00:16:34,159 --> 00:16:35,619
Aku tak tahu. Maaf, ya.

215
00:16:37,621 --> 00:16:38,956
Bicaramu sok akrab.

216
00:16:39,456 --> 00:16:40,457
Pak!

217
00:16:41,417 --> 00:16:43,210
Siapa yang membawanya ke sini?

218
00:16:46,130 --> 00:16:48,257
Aku lebih suka saat dia jadi Su-ji.

219
00:16:49,008 --> 00:16:50,592
Dia lebih buruk dari Bu Choi.

220
00:17:05,524 --> 00:17:07,359
Diantar ke penginapan segala.

221
00:17:09,778 --> 00:17:10,612
Tunggu.

222
00:17:11,864 --> 00:17:14,491
Dia tak akan masuk tiba-tiba, 'kan?

223
00:17:18,287 --> 00:17:19,788
Kau tak mau makan?

224
00:17:21,373 --> 00:17:22,499
Mau!

225
00:17:31,258 --> 00:17:33,469
Sial!

226
00:17:34,303 --> 00:17:36,555
Rasanya kacau sekali.

227
00:17:38,515 --> 00:17:39,641
Aku tak mau makan lagi.

228
00:17:46,106 --> 00:17:47,107
Dia galak, ya?

229
00:17:48,358 --> 00:17:49,443
Ya.

230
00:17:49,526 --> 00:17:52,404
Oh, ya. Mobilmu akan diantar lusa.

231
00:17:53,113 --> 00:17:54,448
Baiklah. Terima kasih.

232
00:17:57,534 --> 00:18:00,662
Omong-omong, apa pekerjaanmu?

233
00:18:02,581 --> 00:18:04,541
- Aku menggambar.
- Apa?

234
00:18:05,125 --> 00:18:05,959
Menggambar?

235
00:18:08,045 --> 00:18:09,171
Kau seniman?

236
00:18:10,380 --> 00:18:12,508
Aku cuma melancong
dan gambar apa yang kusuka.

237
00:18:13,675 --> 00:18:14,635
<i>Seo Mi-rae.</i>

238
00:18:14,718 --> 00:18:17,054
Sekarang giliranmu. Apa tipe idealmu?

239
00:18:17,137 --> 00:18:18,013
Tipe idealku?

240
00:18:18,514 --> 00:18:20,307
Aku suka Gang Dong-won, dia Ju Ji-hoon.

241
00:18:24,228 --> 00:18:25,437
Kalau aku,

242
00:18:25,938 --> 00:18:27,231
pria hibrida.

243
00:18:28,482 --> 00:18:29,316
Apa itu?

244
00:18:30,150 --> 00:18:31,193
Lihatlah.

245
00:18:31,693 --> 00:18:35,114
Seseorang yang punya jiwa murni,

246
00:18:35,197 --> 00:18:37,533
tenang, dan mencintai seni seperti dia.

247
00:18:45,249 --> 00:18:46,542
Jam istirahat masih belajar?

248
00:18:48,210 --> 00:18:50,629
Di sisi lain, dia juga liar dan bebas.

249
00:18:51,713 --> 00:18:52,589
Dia bilang apa?

250
00:18:53,465 --> 00:18:55,092
Jadi, maksudku…

251
00:18:55,175 --> 00:18:58,929
Seperti ada setitik tinta merah
yang bercampur dengan putih…

252
00:18:59,012 --> 00:18:59,847
Paham, 'kan?

253
00:18:59,930 --> 00:19:02,474
Tidak. Apa dia Sinterklas?

254
00:19:03,600 --> 00:19:04,768
Pokoknya begitu.

255
00:19:07,312 --> 00:19:08,856
Seperti itu tipe idealku.

256
00:19:10,566 --> 00:19:11,400
Dua-duanya.

257
00:19:13,735 --> 00:19:17,364
<i>Kami masukkan semua yang kausukai.</i>

258
00:19:20,826 --> 00:19:22,035
Itu bisa diwujudkan?

259
00:19:31,795 --> 00:19:33,130
- Halo.
- Ya.

260
00:19:44,391 --> 00:19:46,852
<i>Perasaan tak bisa berbohong.</i>

261
00:19:47,811 --> 00:19:50,814
Kalau tak suka,
jantungku tenang seperti orang mati.

262
00:19:50,898 --> 00:19:52,149
Paham, 'kan?

263
00:19:52,691 --> 00:19:53,775
Apa maksudmu?

264
00:19:53,859 --> 00:19:55,611
Aku pun mau bersikap santai,

265
00:19:55,694 --> 00:19:58,822
tapi setiap memikirkannya, jantungku…

266
00:19:58,906 --> 00:20:01,992
Berdegup-degup, lalu…

267
00:20:02,075 --> 00:20:04,786
- Paham, 'kan?
- Ini gawat.

268
00:20:04,870 --> 00:20:06,288
Pria seperti apa dia?

269
00:20:06,371 --> 00:20:09,833
Dia memang tipe pria
yang bisa menyedot jiwa wanita, tapi…

270
00:20:09,917 --> 00:20:12,252
Seminggu tak ada kontak, artinya selesai.

271
00:20:12,336 --> 00:20:13,670
Kau ini kenapa?

272
00:20:13,754 --> 00:20:17,257
Produser Kim, cobalah itu.
Untuk menenangkan hatimu.

273
00:20:17,341 --> 00:20:19,635
Sudahlah, tidak perlu.

274
00:20:19,718 --> 00:20:22,137
- Coba apa?
- Boyfriend on Demand.

275
00:20:22,846 --> 00:20:24,890
Ada yang main Boyfriend on Demand?

276
00:20:26,266 --> 00:20:27,100
Serius?

277
00:20:27,601 --> 00:20:30,604
- Kukira hanya sekadar viral.
- Ya, kukira begitu.

278
00:20:30,687 --> 00:20:33,941
Dengan gajiku yang minim,
mau menabung saja sudah berat.

279
00:20:34,024 --> 00:20:36,485
Mana sanggup aku langganan itu?

280
00:20:36,568 --> 00:20:38,528
Teman-temanku banyak yang berlangganan.

281
00:20:38,612 --> 00:20:40,697
- Tidak mungkin.
- Mungkin tidak!

282
00:20:40,781 --> 00:20:42,366
Serius. Coba bayangkan.

283
00:20:42,449 --> 00:20:44,534
Pacaran itu pengeluarannya besar

284
00:20:44,618 --> 00:20:46,620
dan sering kali membuat stres.

285
00:20:47,204 --> 00:20:48,997
Kita bebas dari itu semua. Bagus, 'kan?

286
00:20:49,081 --> 00:20:51,875
Bahkan hidup jadi penggemar idola pun

287
00:20:51,959 --> 00:20:53,627
pengeluarannya sebesar itu.

288
00:20:54,253 --> 00:20:55,587
Kau benar juga.

289
00:20:56,463 --> 00:20:58,632
Ini adalah akhir zaman.

290
00:21:00,592 --> 00:21:01,927
Tidak separah itu…

291
00:21:02,010 --> 00:21:05,764
Kalau dipikir-pikir lagi,
itu harganya 500.000 won, ya?

292
00:21:06,431 --> 00:21:07,474
Ya, benar.

293
00:21:07,975 --> 00:21:10,060
Oke. Biasanya uang 500.000

294
00:21:10,143 --> 00:21:12,980
habis untuk makan,
tiket bioskop, berlibur,

295
00:21:13,063 --> 00:21:14,481
jalan-jalan, dan lainnya.

296
00:21:15,732 --> 00:21:16,900
Boyfriend on Demand?

297
00:21:23,407 --> 00:21:24,241
<i>Sudah kuduga.</i>

298
00:21:24,825 --> 00:21:26,368
<i>Tidak ada reaksi apa-apa.</i>

299
00:21:26,451 --> 00:21:28,787
Coba hubungi dia lagi.

300
00:21:30,872 --> 00:21:32,541
Hubungi dia. Dia tak membicarakanku?

301
00:21:34,418 --> 00:21:35,460
<i>Benar.</i>

302
00:21:35,544 --> 00:21:40,382
<i>Pria yang kutemui kemarin dan Kyeong-nam</i>
<i>adalah orang yang sangat berbeda.</i>

303
00:21:52,811 --> 00:21:53,729
Oke. Dah.

304
00:21:54,855 --> 00:21:55,814
<i>Mereka berbeda.</i>

305
00:22:00,444 --> 00:22:01,486
Bersulang.

306
00:22:07,451 --> 00:22:08,285
Kau tak bosan?

307
00:22:09,745 --> 00:22:10,579
Tidak.

308
00:22:11,455 --> 00:22:13,874
Kenapa duduk saja? Ada pemandangan bagus?

309
00:22:16,501 --> 00:22:17,461
<i>Kau.</i>

310
00:22:29,598 --> 00:22:32,642
Memangnya ini kursi? Kenapa duduk saja?

311
00:22:35,937 --> 00:22:38,273
- Sekarang lebih seru, 'kan?
- Ya.

312
00:22:38,982 --> 00:22:39,983
Berangkat.

313
00:22:40,567 --> 00:22:41,651
Kita jalan!

314
00:22:44,529 --> 00:22:46,156
Kocok-kocok!

315
00:23:10,430 --> 00:23:11,515
Caturangga.

316
00:23:12,599 --> 00:23:13,433
Angkat kepala…

317
00:23:15,102 --> 00:23:16,144
Namaste.

318
00:23:17,813 --> 00:23:19,564
- Namaste.
- Namaste.

319
00:23:20,232 --> 00:23:21,983
Angkat tubuhmu, <i>downward dog</i>.

320
00:23:22,609 --> 00:23:23,735
<i>Downward dog.</i>

321
00:23:23,819 --> 00:23:27,155
- Tapakkan tumitmu ke lantai.
- Baik.

322
00:23:27,239 --> 00:23:29,157
- Caturangga lagi.
- Caturangga.

323
00:23:29,241 --> 00:23:31,910
Angkat kepalamu dan buka hatimu.

324
00:23:31,993 --> 00:23:34,329
Buka hatiku? Harus lebih dekat.

325
00:23:34,413 --> 00:23:36,706
Bukan begitu. Maksudnya buang napas.

326
00:23:41,420 --> 00:23:42,421
Kau suka?

327
00:23:43,922 --> 00:23:44,756
Lepaskan aku!

328
00:23:44,840 --> 00:23:46,925
Tutup mulutmu dan bernapaslah.

329
00:23:47,008 --> 00:23:48,927
- Hentikan!
- Kau harus bernapas.

330
00:23:49,010 --> 00:23:51,847
- Lepaskan.
- Otot paha! Bernapas!

331
00:23:56,977 --> 00:23:59,438
Apa ini? Semuanya gambar pasangan.

332
00:24:00,730 --> 00:24:02,691
Yang lain tak membuatku tertarik.

333
00:24:04,484 --> 00:24:06,778
Seniman yang cuma menggambar pasangan.

334
00:24:07,654 --> 00:24:08,488
Ini menarik.

335
00:24:09,948 --> 00:24:13,160
Tidak semua pasangan kugambar.
Aku punya standar sendiri.

336
00:24:16,163 --> 00:24:19,958
Orang yang tak meragukan masa depan
dan fokus kepada cintanya sekarang.

337
00:24:20,542 --> 00:24:21,585
Itu yang kugambar.

338
00:24:23,503 --> 00:24:24,337
Kenapa?

339
00:24:25,172 --> 00:24:26,131
Entahlah.

340
00:24:29,593 --> 00:24:31,261
Sedih jika cinta berubah.

341
00:24:34,764 --> 00:24:36,183
Jadi aku mengabadikannya.

342
00:24:44,649 --> 00:24:46,860
Masuklah. Sebentar lagi gelap.

343
00:24:52,324 --> 00:24:53,408
Bagaimana, ya?

344
00:24:54,451 --> 00:24:55,285
Apa?

345
00:24:56,453 --> 00:24:59,414
Tadinya aku tak mau bilang,
tapi aku harus jujur.

346
00:25:01,791 --> 00:25:02,626
Apa?

347
00:25:02,709 --> 00:25:03,668
Kita tersesat.

348
00:25:04,461 --> 00:25:05,295
Apa katamu?

349
00:25:15,055 --> 00:25:16,765
Jangan bercanda.

350
00:25:16,848 --> 00:25:18,725
Aku yakin kau tahu jalannya.

351
00:25:19,559 --> 00:25:20,560
Aku serius.

352
00:25:21,061 --> 00:25:24,856
Kata Yu-ra, ada pasangan pengantin baru
yang hilang di sini.

353
00:25:32,656 --> 00:25:34,491
<i>Apa genre film favoritmu?</i>

354
00:25:35,825 --> 00:25:37,744
HOROR (TERUTAMA HOROR GAIB!)

355
00:25:37,827 --> 00:25:38,912
<i>Orang-orang itu!</i>

356
00:25:39,412 --> 00:25:41,790
<i>Aku suka film begitu,</i>
<i>bukan berarti mau mengalaminya.</i>

357
00:25:42,290 --> 00:25:43,124
Aku…

358
00:25:43,625 --> 00:25:46,127
Aku tak mau di sini. Ayo pergi…

359
00:26:02,352 --> 00:26:03,353
Anjing pemilik rumah.

360
00:26:04,563 --> 00:26:05,605
Oh, ya.

361
00:26:07,732 --> 00:26:10,777
- Kau setakut itu?
- Tidak, cuma…

362
00:26:11,278 --> 00:26:12,112
Sedikit.

363
00:26:13,446 --> 00:26:15,240
Di sini memang gelap.

364
00:26:40,390 --> 00:26:41,308
Sudah terang?

365
00:27:04,414 --> 00:27:07,042
<i>Coba dulu. Kau pasti berubah pikiran.</i>

366
00:27:07,876 --> 00:27:09,252
Tenanglah.

367
00:27:09,794 --> 00:27:11,254
Hei, tenang!

368
00:27:13,757 --> 00:27:15,342
<i>Pintu ditutup.</i>

369
00:27:25,101 --> 00:27:26,686
<i>Pintu dibuka.</i>

370
00:27:27,270 --> 00:27:29,731
Permisi. Mohon maaf.

371
00:27:29,814 --> 00:27:31,691
Mohon maaf.

372
00:27:33,234 --> 00:27:34,944
Maaf.

373
00:27:35,028 --> 00:27:36,696
<i>Pintu ditutup.</i>

374
00:27:47,916 --> 00:27:49,417
Seo Mi-rae, ke ruanganku.

375
00:27:50,335 --> 00:27:51,586
Hei, Kyeong-nam.

376
00:27:51,670 --> 00:27:52,837
Kau juga.

377
00:27:54,130 --> 00:27:55,882
<i>Kau sudah bilang Yun Song?</i>

378
00:27:56,466 --> 00:27:57,300
Ya?

379
00:27:57,884 --> 00:27:58,718
Soal apa?

380
00:27:59,302 --> 00:28:01,429
Katanya Kyeong-nam sudah bilang.

381
00:28:02,555 --> 00:28:05,433
Iklan perabot itu
akan dikerjakan oleh Hwany.

382
00:28:06,851 --> 00:28:07,727
Belum?

383
00:28:08,770 --> 00:28:11,189
Maaf. Aku akan segera mengabarinya.

384
00:28:11,773 --> 00:28:13,858
Kau tahu Bu Yun! Kalau baru bilang…

385
00:28:13,942 --> 00:28:15,151
Astaga!

386
00:28:16,444 --> 00:28:20,365
Selain itu, kau dijadwalkan hadir
di FKB dengan Bu Yun, 'kan?

387
00:28:20,448 --> 00:28:22,534
Kyeong-nam dan Hwany juga ikut.

388
00:28:23,743 --> 00:28:26,246
- Apa?
- Itu alasanku memanggilmu.

389
00:28:27,664 --> 00:28:29,708
Kali ini, keduanya dinominasikan.

390
00:28:30,750 --> 00:28:32,168
- Hwany juga?
- Ya.

391
00:28:33,211 --> 00:28:36,297
Firasatku, salah satunya akan menang.

392
00:28:36,381 --> 00:28:38,341
Jadi, perhatikan penulis kalian.

393
00:28:39,050 --> 00:28:40,719
- Mengerti?
- Ya.

394
00:28:41,553 --> 00:28:42,387
Baik.

395
00:28:50,979 --> 00:28:51,813
Kalau begitu…

396
00:28:54,691 --> 00:28:57,444
Tolong sampaikan kepada Bu Yun.
Dia pasti marah.

397
00:28:59,112 --> 00:29:01,197
Tidak apa-apa. Akan kusampaikan.

398
00:29:01,906 --> 00:29:02,991
Produser Seo.

399
00:29:03,908 --> 00:29:04,909
Ya?

400
00:29:07,829 --> 00:29:08,830
Ada apa denganmu?

401
00:29:10,290 --> 00:29:11,958
Apa… Apa maksudmu?

402
00:29:12,834 --> 00:29:15,044
Aku yang ditolak,
tapi kau yang menghindar.

403
00:29:17,881 --> 00:29:20,175
Aku tak menghindar. Kapan aku begitu?

404
00:29:21,342 --> 00:29:23,261
Aku tahu kau tidak nyaman,

405
00:29:24,679 --> 00:29:26,222
tapi jangan terang-terangan.

406
00:29:29,601 --> 00:29:31,060
Aku juga merasa sedih.

407
00:29:47,577 --> 00:29:49,287
<i>Hei, kau sudah gila?</i>

408
00:29:49,370 --> 00:29:51,998
- Kenapa diberikan kepadanya?
<i>- Sebenarnya…</i>

409
00:29:52,081 --> 00:29:53,666
Ini permintaan pengiklan.

410
00:29:53,750 --> 00:29:57,462
Maksudnya lebih baik
pakai gambar jelek itu dibanding gambarku?

411
00:29:57,545 --> 00:29:58,755
Apa mereka bodoh?

412
00:29:58,838 --> 00:30:02,217
Bu Yun, aku janji akan dapatkan
iklan yang lebih bagus…

413
00:30:04,260 --> 00:30:05,136
Ditutup.

414
00:30:06,930 --> 00:30:08,890
Ini benar-benar mengesalkan!

415
00:30:15,563 --> 00:30:17,690
<i>Perabot terbaik itu dari IG. Ya, 'kan?</i>

416
00:30:18,191 --> 00:30:20,819
<i>Webtun kolaborasi </i>PlanC <i>dan IG</i>
<i>akan segera hadir.</i>

417
00:30:20,902 --> 00:30:22,028
<i>Kuusahakan yang terbaik!</i>

418
00:30:22,612 --> 00:30:24,197
PlanC<i>, ayo jadi nomor satu!</i>

419
00:30:24,280 --> 00:30:25,323
"Nomor satu"?

420
00:30:26,032 --> 00:30:27,659
Bocah tengik ini…

421
00:30:39,546 --> 00:30:40,421
Bersulang!

422
00:30:44,717 --> 00:30:47,011
Aku sudah muak dengan makanan berkrim.

423
00:30:49,430 --> 00:30:50,598
Aku rindu rasa ini!

424
00:30:50,682 --> 00:30:51,975
Kencanmu lancar?

425
00:30:53,059 --> 00:30:54,602
Entahlah, semuanya kacau.

426
00:30:54,686 --> 00:30:56,855
Kencan dua kali sehari itu berlebihan.

427
00:30:56,938 --> 00:31:00,400
Rute mereka bersilangan,
jadi tak sengaja berpapasan.

428
00:31:02,443 --> 00:31:04,612
Sudah kuduga akan kacau.

429
00:31:04,696 --> 00:31:07,782
Tapi beberapa hari setelahnya,
aku kencan buta lagi.

430
00:31:10,034 --> 00:31:12,245
Aku benar-benar tidak habis pikir.

431
00:31:12,829 --> 00:31:16,124
Dia menanyakan gajiku
dimulai dari angka tiga atau empat.

432
00:31:16,207 --> 00:31:17,083
Gila.

433
00:31:17,166 --> 00:31:19,544
Memangnya untuk apa dia tahu itu?

434
00:31:20,044 --> 00:31:22,088
Besoknya, tahu apa isi pesannya?

435
00:31:22,797 --> 00:31:26,134
"Aku tersentuh mendengar ceritamu
soal mencari jati diri.

436
00:31:26,217 --> 00:31:28,261
Semoga kau bertemu orang yang tepat."

437
00:31:28,344 --> 00:31:29,554
Gila.

438
00:31:29,637 --> 00:31:32,932
Itu seperti pesan
tak lulus wawancara dari SDM.

439
00:31:33,016 --> 00:31:35,977
Aku tak pernah melamar kerja kepada dia.
Mengesalkan!

440
00:31:36,060 --> 00:31:39,355
Astaga. Sudahlah, berhenti kencan buta.

441
00:31:39,439 --> 00:31:40,940
Mereka selalu membuatmu marah.

442
00:31:41,024 --> 00:31:44,819
Kau sudah lihat sendiri.
Tidak ada lagi pria yang ideal.

443
00:31:45,904 --> 00:31:49,866
Kau dan aku adalah burung
yang bangun kesiangan.

444
00:31:49,949 --> 00:31:55,038
Sekarang kita harus mengais-ngais
sisa makanan dari burung yang rajin.

445
00:31:55,121 --> 00:31:57,874
Memangnya harus sampai mengais-ngais?

446
00:31:59,584 --> 00:32:00,418
Hei.

447
00:32:01,169 --> 00:32:03,588
Kau mau mengecapku sebagai penggila pria?

448
00:32:03,671 --> 00:32:06,090
Hei, bukan itu maksudku.

449
00:32:06,174 --> 00:32:07,550
Lalu apa maksudmu?

450
00:32:07,634 --> 00:32:10,803
"Tak bisa hidup tanpa pria?
Aku muak mendengarmu membahas pria."

451
00:32:10,887 --> 00:32:12,013
Begitu, 'kan?

452
00:32:12,096 --> 00:32:14,766
Karena sejak tadi
kau cuma membicarakan itu.

453
00:32:14,849 --> 00:32:18,561
Apa kau tak pernah membahas pria?
Bagaimana soal pria di kantormu itu?

454
00:32:19,479 --> 00:32:22,148
Hei, apa maksudmu? Dia cuma rekan kerja.

455
00:32:22,231 --> 00:32:25,610
Sejak beberapa bulan lalu,
kau sering membicarakannya.

456
00:32:26,194 --> 00:32:27,570
Apa? Tidak pernah!

457
00:32:27,654 --> 00:32:29,864
Aku tak membicarakannya sesering itu.

458
00:32:32,408 --> 00:32:35,745
Tadinya aku mau tunggu kau cerita sendiri,
tapi tak bisa.

459
00:32:36,245 --> 00:32:37,246
Kau suka dia, 'kan?

460
00:32:38,831 --> 00:32:41,292
Hei, kau sudah gila? Tidak!

461
00:32:47,048 --> 00:32:47,924
Kebalikannya.

462
00:32:48,591 --> 00:32:50,927
Kebalikannya? Apa maksudmu?

463
00:32:51,886 --> 00:32:52,971
Sebenarnya,

464
00:32:53,805 --> 00:32:55,932
dia menyatakan cinta kepadaku.

465
00:32:57,517 --> 00:32:59,310
Hei!

466
00:33:01,145 --> 00:33:03,648
Kenapa berita besar itu baru kauceritakan?

467
00:33:03,731 --> 00:33:04,857
Itu kapan?

468
00:33:04,941 --> 00:33:08,069
Sudah lama. Aku sudah menolaknya juga.

469
00:33:10,196 --> 00:33:11,030
Tidak mungkin.

470
00:33:12,573 --> 00:33:14,325
